# DSP-LAB-10

#ADDITION USING DIRECT ADDRESSSING MODE

PROGRAM:

 INP1    .SET 0H 
INP2    .SET 1H 
OUT     .SET 2H 
.mmregs 
.text 
START: 
LD   #140H,DP 
RSBX   CPL 
NOP 
NOP 
NOP 
NOP 
LD       INP1,A 
ADD    INP2,A 
STL      A,OUT 
HLT:   B HLT 

INPUT:

 Data Memory:
 A000h  0004 
A001h  0004 

OUTPUT:

 Data Memory : 
A002h  0008
